:"domain";s:16:"pt.pinterest.com";}i:19;a:11:{s:7:"keyword";s:33:"chair yoga for seniors with music";s:4:"slug";s:33:"chair-yoga-for-seniors-with-music";s:5:"title";s:93:"Vibrant Aging Yoga Seated Yoga Series With Tatis Cervantes Aiken Chair Yoga Yoga Partner Yoga";s:3:"alt";s:93:"vibrant aging yoga seated yoga series with tatis cervantes aiken chair yoga yoga partner yoga";s:3:"url";s:76:"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/59/25/00/592500a55f12a327c223978e57ffe9a6.jpg";s:5:"thumb";s:123:"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSrr2GIPiVNZwnZyaRtrGLeKG0nmuOniyIJmjU8qgLQB05PFsZ7poQTgCNhl1gyVEyb0p0";s:8:"filetype";s:3:"jpg";s:5:"width";i:720;s:6:"height";i:1280;s:6:"source";s:49:"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/422071796328520314/";s:6:"domain";s:17:"www.pinterest.com";}i:20;a:11:{s:7:"keyword";s:33:"chair yoga for seniors with music";s:4:"slug";s:33:"chair-yoga-for-seniors-with-music";s:5:"title";s:10:"Pin On Fit";s:3:"alt";s:10:"pin on fit";s:3:"url";s:52:"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/5kGf2bRAlY0/maxresdefault.jpg";s:5:"thumb";s:90:"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcRXCgUzmYBAIWAixB66ICdH87Ccb6aMYS7LDg";s:8:"filetype";s:3:"jpg";s:5:"width";i:720;s:6:"height";i:1280;s:6:"source";s:49:"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/549017010826925088/";s:6:"domain";s:17:"www.pinterest.com";}}s:9:"sentences";a:62:{i:0;s:99:"It also reduces anxiety helps lower blood pressure protects joints and builds strength and balance.";i:1;s:103:"We found a fantastic 30 minute routine of gentle chair yoga for seniors thats free to watch on YouTube.";i:2;s:89:"Instructor Sherry Zak Morris makes the class fun and lively and explains the benefits of.";i:3;s:123:"Gentle chair yoga and gentle yoga standing poses are low impact and can help strengthen your muscles and improve your mood.";i:4;s:89:"The benefits of yoga include lower stress levels reduced inflammation and decreased pain.";i:5;s:134:"A study published in the Journal of the American Geriatrics Society examined the effects of chair yoga in seniors with osteoarthritis.";i:6;s:27:"The study consisted of 131.";i:7;s:24:"Call us at 917-370-5787.";i:8;s:115:"ElderChair Yoga founded by Lynn Lehmkuhl RYT has been serving New York City with chair yoga for seniors since 2014.";i:9;s:100:"She offers seated low-impact yoga workouts in-home and on-site at senior centers and places of work.";i:10;s:91:"Lynn is highly skilled and experienced in working with seniors and the physically impaired.";i:11;s:16:"Are You In Pain.";i:12;s:22:"What is a Pain Doctor.";i:13;s:24:"What is Pain Management.";i:14;s:19:"Acute Chronic Pain.";i:15;s:32:"Chair yoga Yoga is for everyone.";i:16;s:28:"Any age or state of fitness.";i:17;s:49:"Yoga can calm your mind and strengthen your body.";i:18;s:49:"These chair poses can be done at work or at home.";i:19;s:79:"Directions Most positions begin using the same seated position called Sit tall.";i:20;s:90:"Sit in a chair with feet planted firmly on the floor Back straight to elongate your spine.";i:21;s:93:"To help you find music seniors love weve rounded up dozens of top hits from every generation.";i:22;s:48:"Music reaches those with Alzheimers or dementia.";i:23;s:104:"Another benefit is that music helps people reminisce and go back and relate to emotions and experiences.";i:24;s:71:"Thats why its often recommended for people with Alzheimers or dementia.";i:25;s:69:"It reduces anxiety and agitation and boosts happiness and engagement.";i:26;s:136:"Perfect for seniors Chair Yoga is a seated exercise class that raises the heart rate and improves balance with minimal impact on joints.";i:27;s:98:"This class taught by an instructor who is in the Shape Up NYC Fitness Instructor Training Program.";i:28;s:65:"This class occurs every Friday from 11a noon starting in January.";i:29;s:90:"By improving strength and flexibility chair yoga for seniors can help seniors avoid falls.";i:30;s:228:"Seniors with disabilities weight challenges inflexibility or a lack of floor to standing mobility who cannot practice traditional yoga may benefit from frequent chair yoga for seniors whether at home at a class or at the office.";i:31;s:82:"Even a wheelchair-bound senior can receive chair yogas benefits such as mind-body.";i:32;s:77:"With all of that said here are some examples of chair yoga poses for seniors.";i:33;s:34:"Extend arms straight into the air.";i:34;s:49:"Press palms together forming the tip of a candle.";i:35;s:20:"Hold for 30 seconds.";i:36;s:18:"Raised Hands Pose.";i:37;s:34:"Extend arms straight into the air.";i:38;s:40:"If possible extend legs forward as well.";i:39;s:25:"Hold pose for 30 seconds.";i:40;s:18:"Forward Bend Pose.";i:41;s:157:"Chair yoga for seniors Chair yoga is a versatile prop that allows the practitioner to refine their movements and be more mindful without the fear of falling.";i:42;s:118:"It is also an excellent tool to isolate the top half of the body from the bottom half allowing greater access to each.";i:43;s:48:"Chair Yoga - Yoga For Seniors Yoga With Adriene.";i:44;s:115:"Chair Yoga invites you to find mobility in a way that is soft and gentle but also really supportive and beneficial.";i:45;s:102:"This 17 min practice invites awareness and integrity into the body specifically the line of the spine.";i:46;s:79:"Activate the muscles that help you find length up through the spine for better.";i:47;s:171:"For people hindered by age stiffness or injury chair yoga for seniors is the perfect way to ease into the practice without pushing your body to do more than it can handle.";i:48;s:98:"Chair yoga comes with the same benefits that yoga has so it is by no means a watered-down version.";i:49;s:67:"Furthermore older adults stand to benefit the most from activities.";i:50;s:133:"Many senior chair yoga students who previously experienced chronic constipation have more regular bowel movements without medication.";i:51;s:141:"Pain from arthritis sciatica chronic backache and other conditions also tends to decrease or in some cases even disappear with yoga practice.";i:52;s:100:"Feb 21 2017 - Explore Laura Selins board Chair yoga for Seniors followed by 115 people on Pinterest.";i:53;s:54:"See more ideas about yoga for seniors chair yoga yoga.";i:54;s:87:"Amazons Choice for chair yoga for seniors Yoga for Seniors with Jane Adams 2nd edition.";i:55;s:91:"Improve Balance Strength Flexibility with Gentle Senior Yoga now with 3 complete practices.";i:56;s:23:"46 out of 5 stars 1931.";i:57;s:139:"Chair yoga for seniors comes to Florence County Classes started this week and run through the middle of December The chair is designed for.";i:58;s:32:"Adaptive Chair Yoga for Seniors.";i:59;s:116:"In addition to the various types of yoga adaptive practices help seniors with even very limited mobility to do yoga.";i:60;s:32:"Adaptive yoga practices include.";i:61;s:103:"Chair Yoga Ideal for those who cannot stand for long periods of time or who cannot work on a floor mat.";}}